title: GOContacts Theme Color Minimal v1.1
description:
his is a Color Minimal Theme for GO Contacts Ex.

Make sure to check out my matching Go SMS Pro Color Minimal theme!
This is NOT a standalone app, so download Go Contacts Ex in the market if you haven't already done so.
Installation
1. Install GO Contacts Ex (free & available in the Market)
2. Install this theme
3. Menu -> Themes -> Color Minimal Theme
